-- Turkey's Erdogan Says Germany Has Problem with `Islamophobia,' Immigrants
-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 2010-10-20T11:08:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/turkey-s-erdogan-says-germany-has-problem-with-islamophobia-immigrants.html
Turkish Prime Minister Recep Tayyip
Erdogan said Germany has a problem with “Islamophobia” and
multi-culturalism should be seen as contributing to a nation’s
richness.  Erdogan was speaking in Helsinki at a news conference with
Finnish Prime Minister Mari Kiviniemi today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
